Description: PF-style control plane for Linux networking
 OCaml-first firewall policy control plane targeting nftables,
 policy routing, tc, conntrack, and NFLOG. Provides readable
 policy files, safe atomic apply with rollback, packet decision
 explainability, policy tests, dynamic tables, and multi-backend
 diff/live readback.
